<p class="ayah 23-52" id="52" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَإِنَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And indeed</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">هَـٰذِهِۦٓ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">this,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أُمَّتُكُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">your religion,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أُمَّةً</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) religion</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٲحِدَةً</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">one.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَأَنَا۟</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And I Am</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">رَبُّكُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">your Lord,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَٱتَّقُونِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">so fear Me.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>52<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
