<p class="ayah 23-58" id="58" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱلَّذِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And those</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">هُم</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">[they]</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِـَٔـايَـٰتِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">in (the) Signs</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">رَبِّهِمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) their Lord</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يُؤْمِنُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">believe</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>58<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 23-59" id="59" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱلَّذِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And those</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">هُم</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">[they]</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِرَبِّهِمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">with their Lord</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(do) not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يُشْرِكُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">associate partners.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>59<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 23-60" id="60" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱلَّذِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And those who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يُؤْتُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">give</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَآ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">what</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ءَاتَواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they give</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَّقُلُوبُهُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">while their hearts</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَجِلَةٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(are) fearful,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَنَّهُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">because they</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَىٰ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">رَبِّهِمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">their Lord</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">رَٲجِعُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(will) return</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>60<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
