<p class="ayah 23-89" id="89" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">سَيَقُولُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">They will say,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِلَّهِ‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">"Allah."</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قُلْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Say,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَأَنَّىٰ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">"Then how</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تُسْحَرُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">are you deluded?"</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>89<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
